query2:Top 3 customers by total spend+
--------------------------------------
Sql query Top 3 customers by total spend:
SELECT  c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name,
SUM(s.total_amount) AS total_spend
FROM customers c
JOIN sales s
ON c.customer_id = s.customer_id
GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name
ORDER BY total_spend DESC
LIMIT 3;
--------------------------------------------------
query3:Top 3 customers by total spend
--------------------------------------------------
pyspark query Top 3 customers by total spend:
joined_df = customers.join(orders, "customer_id", "left")
df = (
    joined_df.groupBy("customer_id", "first_name", "last_name")
    .agg(coalesce(sum("total_amount"), lit(0)).alias("total_order_amount"))
